<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite poklopac stupa upravljača. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A6206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
